    "name": "极累冥途",
    "steam_appid": 3078920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了应对人均寿命暴增带来的负面影响，地府转型成为了快递部门。凭着廉价、高效很快做大做强。可一场可乐配送事故让无数错喝孟婆汤丢了魂的打工人流入黄泉。把地府挤了个水泄不通。滞留的快递和魂魄被孤魂野鬼分了个精光。求人不如求己，失忆的打工人必须面对各种妖魔鬼怪，扎进快递堆中捞回属于自己的那份魂魄。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/4cc4cc4e1d09126128672969979153d9.poster.avif?t=1745568872\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/4cc4cc4e1d09126128672969979153d9.webm?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/4cc4cc4e1d09126128672969979153d9.mp4?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开工大吉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冥府上班可没那么简单，小心那些魑魅魍魉，除了你的同行，他们是真想要你的命，通过击杀它们换取功德从签筒中抽取强力术法来强化自身，为各位在冥界工作顺利进行，我们精心挑选了超多术法，其中包括但不限于选取次数有限的核心与辅助技能，更有多达55个不占栏位的特殊被动提供增幅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/9f843ff42fd5843552af45b697b04200.poster.avif?t=1745568872\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/9f843ff42fd5843552af45b697b04200.webm?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/9f843ff42fd5843552af45b697b04200.mp4?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >术数无常，吉凶难料。吉签自留，凶签扔掉。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在诸位工作之时，也有人在地府上下打点关系，千挑万选之后定下15种扰乱之术，但凡事皆有代价，这份“便利”也不是平白无故给到各位，每次升级诸位都将获得“三吉一凶”，当你的同行遇到困难之时，说不定.....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小小凶签可能有大大作用。</strong>      </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/16a1bd62fa1f3f974f57c52d08335b2d.poster.avif?t=1745568872\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/16a1bd62fa1f3f974f57c52d08335b2d.webm?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/16a1bd62fa1f3f974f57c52d08335b2d.mp4?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>改命</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >什么？这不是你生前的记忆？没关系，“贴心”的孟婆为你准备了短效孟婆汤，一碗下肚，即刻转职。在游戏初期，我们共为大家准备了6种不同的职业，相信总有一种能够助你在游戏中取得自己的记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/6a1d3e837a70a3a665e794cb1ecea051.poster.avif?t=1745568872\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/6a1d3e837a70a3a665e794cb1ecea051.webm?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078920/extras/6a1d3e837a70a3a665e794cb1ecea051.mp4?t=1745568872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >请神</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冥府里也藏着各路神仙，每位神仙都有着自己的风格与变数，尝试找回丢失的信件或许能够换得他们助力，可别小看这些助力，他可能会让你在怪潮之中杀出重围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>最后的最后，请各位路途当心，你的对手除了孤魂野鬼，也可能是其他失魂落魄的打工人~</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
